WEBVTT

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.350
Good morning, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.510
joining us again tonight. We really

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:08.070
appreciate it. We're just reading

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:10.230
this book, "In Him,"by Brother

00:00:10.230 --> 00:00:10.240
Kenneth

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:13.270
E.

00:00:13.270 --> 00:00:13.280
Hagin.

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:15.110
Dad Hagin always had the

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:18.070
nuggets. I just go over and over

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.590
all these books. She got a whole bunch

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:23.910
more this week.

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:34.950
Well, thank you for joining me today,

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:35.590
Diana.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.350
Yes,

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:41.270
I wanted to go over some things, but

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:42.790
I was going to have you see what

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:44.229
questions they asked. You can look at

00:00:44.239 --> 00:00:47.670
it. Do you have any questions? You know,

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:49.590
I never really just open it up with

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:51.670
questions, but I'll go over some of the

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:53.750
things we talked about this last

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:57.430
prayer session. I took the time to

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.990
really pray over what the Lord has

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:02.069
been showing me because of the

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:05.990
persecution that was brought with it.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.990
And the Lord said, "Braden, I told

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.910
you you were called to say the hard

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.950
things, and the ones that say they

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.469
really like you, there'll be times when

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:16.870
they turn against you because of what I

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:19.670
have you say."And he went over and

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:22.710
he was talking about

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:26.630
the prophet talking to David. The

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:27.190
prophet

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:30.550
Nathan

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:34.310
went and told David something very hard.

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:38.149
But David was loved amongst the people.

00:01:38.159 --> 00:01:39.830
Everybody loved David. David was the

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:43.270
man. But nobody knew what was going on

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:45.830
behind closed doors.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:48.870
When the men were out to war, David

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:51.190
was at home looking at naked women on

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:54.069
the balcony, messing around and doing

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:56.710
things. But it wasn't a popular thing.

00:01:56.720 --> 00:02:00.310
But Nathan pulled David aside privately

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:03.270
and said, "This is what the Lord has to

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:05.270
say to

00:02:05.270 --> 00:02:05.280
you."And

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:09.029
sometimes, out of what I

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:11.190
believe the Lord gives me, are these

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.949
words

00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:16.869
of warning, words of affirmation,

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:20.869
words of

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:23.830
correction

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:26.630
that are not always easy to give. But

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:28.229
Nathan did it, and it wasn't the easy

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:31.430
thing to do because David was popular.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:34.390
David was loved. But nobody knew what

00:02:34.400 --> 00:02:37.110
was going on behind David's door when no

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:40.070
one was looking.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:42.550
And sometimes we can see

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:45.190
people. I'm not accusing anybody of

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:48.869
anything. I only hear in

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:52.229
part, I see in part. And sometimes

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:54.869
whenever a voice like mine speaks

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:57.190
against somebody that is very pretty

00:02:57.190 --> 00:02:57.200
with

00:02:57.200 --> 00:03:00.150
pretty eyes and you say this is

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:02.390
what's coming and storms and things like

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.190
that, people get really ticked off at

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:08.309
you because you touch their pets, the

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:10.550
things that are important to them.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:13.030
But the Lord is saying, "I have this

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:17.110
to say regardless."Then I say, just like

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:21.670
Saul, Saul was a bad man, was killing

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:25.110
Christians and was wrong, was awful, and

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.790
the prophet didn't even want to go and

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:29.509
pray for him after he went blind. He

00:03:29.509 --> 00:03:29.519
was

00:03:29.519 --> 00:03:32.789
scared for his life.

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:34.550
But the Lord said, "Go and pray for him

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:37.270
and I'll restore his sight."It wasn't an

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:40.710
easy thing. But he spoke and said, "This

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:44.550
is what God said."But Paul, that was

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.270
Saul, turned around and was one of the

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:51.350
greatest voices of the Bible. And

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.430
so, you know, it's not always easy. And

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:56.390
like I tell you all, I see Candace and I

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:58.630
saw all these things.

00:03:58.640 --> 00:04:00.630
I don't know what she stands for. I do

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:03.030
not watch her program.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:05.910
I personally see darkness.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:09.509
But the Lord said that he had a plan for

00:04:09.519 --> 00:04:12.710
her life. And I want you to speak this

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:15.589
in and make it public that I have a plan

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:18.789
for her to go before a major door.

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:21.110
And I've prayed over what I've told

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:23.830
you all immensely.

00:04:23.840 --> 00:04:26.070
I'm talking more prayer over this than

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.629
I've prayed over a lot of things because

00:04:28.639 --> 00:04:31.909
of how heavy the word was

00:04:31.919 --> 00:04:35.430
and what I had said publicly. And I take

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:39.110
this very

00:04:39.110 --> 00:04:39.120
seriously

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:42.390
that I speak and I see

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:44.469
and I deliver words accurately and

00:04:44.479 --> 00:04:46.870
they're not in the flesh. Regardless of how

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.350
it's liked or how it's disliked, I am

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:52.870
not working for you. I'm working for Him

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:55.670
and I'm sold out to Him. And it's

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:57.430
just like when I went to that pastor

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:01.189
before and I said, "Sir, if you don't

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:04.310
repent and change, your whole church

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:07.029
is going down within a couple

00:05:07.029 --> 00:05:07.039
months."Not

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:09.350
knowing that he was committing

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:12.070
adultery on his wife the whole time.

00:05:12.070 --> 00:05:12.080
He

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.870
lost everything and the building and the

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.550
church doesn't even exist now. And it

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:18.710
was a $20 million

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.629
building.

00:05:20.639 --> 00:05:24.070
$20 million. And it was paid off. He lost

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:27.830
the congregation, lost it all.

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:30.390
I've given some real dandy

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:32.710
words where I thought they were going to

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:36.070
egg me on my way out of the building,

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:39.110
but I've given them and I was bold. I've

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:41.189
done it three times to three ministers,

00:05:41.199 --> 00:05:43.430
and each one of them has fallen

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:45.990
with adultery.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:48.550
Every single one of them. And every

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:50.310
single one of them, the Lord said, "I'm

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:52.550
warning you to change.

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:54.870
I want you to repent and change and come

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:57.749
back to my heart."And every one of them

00:05:57.749 --> 00:05:57.759
was

00:05:57.759 --> 00:06:00.150
accurate,

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:03.990
and I know His voice. So when I warn you

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:08.390
about the things I'm warning you about,

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:10.070
just pray about it if you don't believe

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:13.670
it because I can miss it. We're all

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.909
human. I'm not trying to justify and say,

00:06:15.919 --> 00:06:17.670
"Well, Brandon's always right."I'm not

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.390
always right. I'm just as human as

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:22.950
all of you are. But I just keep

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:26.070
seeking His face. So if I say the

00:06:26.080 --> 00:06:28.230
Lord wants to use Candace in the future

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:30.150
with maybe a Senate position or

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:32.469
something huge in government, then we

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:33.909
need to pray for her because that means

00:06:33.919 --> 00:06:36.070
His hand is on her to do something. Does

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:38.309
she stand against the Jews? From what I

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:41.830
understand, yes. I don't agree

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:43.110
that I stand with the Jews

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.270
wholeheartedly. I pray for the Jews. I

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:47.510
pray for the peace of Jerusalem. Do I

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:49.749
stand with the government of Israel all

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:52.710
the time? No, I don't. Just like I

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:54.309
don't stand with our government, but I

00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:57.110
still pray for them. Do I like what

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.870
the Democrats do when Joe Biden's in

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:01.749
power or Obama? No. When Obama won the

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:05.670
second term, I wept myself to sleep.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.990
I'll never forget when Mitt Romney lost

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.390
and I was sitting there going, "What are we

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:12.230
going into for another four

00:07:12.230 --> 00:07:12.240
years?"When

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.830
people were rejoicing, going, "Oh, four

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:15.270
more years,"they were so excited and I was

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:17.670
like, "Oh God, our country is coming to

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:21.029
an end."But God had His hand on it and

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:22.550
brought us through,

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:25.350
and we still prayed for him.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:28.230
But even in the midst of me

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:31.589
telling you what I saw about Candace,

00:07:31.599 --> 00:07:35.749
God can turn a Saul into a Paul.

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:36.950
Did I say that right? Yes.

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.510
Sometimes I go, "You got a

00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:45.430
filter? What is it?"But the

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:49.510
Lord showed me what He showed me. But is

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:49.520
it

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:51.990
the rabbit hole? And I'll say this and

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:54.550
close with this because we got to move

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:57.029
on. Is the rabbit hole that He said

00:07:57.039 --> 00:07:58.869
don't keep going down because it

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:01.110
will cost you your life? Is it your life

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.790
of what He's wanting to do or is it

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:07.990
physically? Some things are metaphors.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.629
Stop looking down the rabbit hole. I

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:13.029
have more for you to do. Don't keep

00:08:13.039 --> 00:08:15.670
going down these conspiracies.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:18.309
Don't keep going down this stuff. I have

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:22.390
more for you to do behind another door.

00:08:22.400 --> 00:08:26.629
It will cost you your future.

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:29.270
So, is this a warning of life and

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:32.630
death or is this a warning about a career?

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.389
That's for her to decide. That's

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.310
not my business. I just deliver the

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.909
word. But then people go, "Well, are you

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:39.589
threatening? What is that

00:08:39.589 --> 00:08:39.599
saying?"I

00:08:39.599 --> 00:08:41.750
don't know, folks. I just

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:43.829
deliver the word. But I know that the

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:46.710
Lord said He had more for her to do

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:49.350
according to what the Lord is saying.

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.430
You know what? He sees the heart of the

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:53.030
individual and He sees that

00:08:53.040 --> 00:08:54.949
there's potential there to do something

00:08:54.959 --> 00:08:56.870
major for Him and be a mouthpiece for

00:08:56.880 --> 00:09:00.150
Him. Do I agree with everything she

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:01.910
says? I don't even know what the woman

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.990
says.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:06.949
So, I have to say that I want to make

00:09:06.959 --> 00:09:09.750
that very clear, but Brandon Biggs

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:12.630
just delivers the hard things and it's

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:14.150
not always easy standing on this side of

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:16.310
the camera,

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:18.790
and I appreciate your

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:21.269
prayers. If you don't agree with what I

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:26.070
say, pray for me. Please pray for me

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:27.910
because I'm just as human as you

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:30.949
are. And in that, I ask you to give me

00:09:30.959 --> 00:09:33.990
grace whenever I give a word across a

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:36.389
camera that is very hard for me to even

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:38.949
give. It takes a lot of courage to stand

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:40.790
on this side and tell that there's going

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:43.269
to be another Watergate and that JD

00:09:43.279 --> 00:09:45.590
Vance is going to be at the helm of it.

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:48.230
It's not easy to say that. The Lord said

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:50.550
it hasn't happened yet, but there's

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:53.829
coming a day when JD Vance

00:09:53.829 --> 00:09:53.839
will—this

00:09:53.839 --> 00:09:55.910
would be very bad. And you must

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:58.790
pray for this nation because

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.750
if this would happen, it would

00:10:01.760 --> 00:10:04.550
derail something very bad.

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.550
Something very bad would happen. And the

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:08.630
Lord said, "You must pray for his heart,

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:11.269
for he's not who he says he is in the

00:10:11.269 --> 00:10:11.279
future."Now,

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:14.150
what would happen? Just

00:10:14.160 --> 00:10:17.030
like we saw Amy Coney

00:10:17.030 --> 00:10:17.040
Barrett,

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:19.509
we all thought she was great and it was

00:10:19.519 --> 00:10:22.230
going to be awesome. But as she goes,

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.470
the bitterness and the hardness of the

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:28.230
position makes you change.

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:31.430
If you're not word-based

00:10:31.440 --> 00:10:33.110
and you are not rooted and

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.509
grounded in love, power and

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:38.389
responsibility change you because your

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:43.430
character wasn't there to handle it. To

00:10:43.430 --> 00:10:43.440
whom

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:45.750
much is given, much is required.

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:49.110
And if JD Vance got to be president,

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:53.750
I saw a different man. What changes a

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:56.870
man is pressure,

00:10:56.880 --> 00:10:58.630
but it was always there. It's like

00:10:58.640 --> 00:11:01.750
people say money ruins a man. No, the

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:03.509
man was already ruined before he got the

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:05.350
money. The money just magnified who he

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:07.910
was.

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:10.470
Does that make sense what I'm

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:12.790
saying? It's not the money; it's

00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:15.269
the character of the man already. So

00:11:15.279 --> 00:11:16.630
that's what I'm trying to tell you all:

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:19.350
I'm seeing these things. And then I

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:24.389
saw, and then I heard, a Monica

00:11:24.389 --> 00:11:24.399
Lewinsky-Marilyn

00:11:24.399 --> 00:11:29.350
Monroe scandal,

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:34.310
and then I heard "before a

00:11:34.310 --> 00:11:34.320
storm"and

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.550
all these things. So, I just wanted

00:11:36.560 --> 00:11:39.910
to try to

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:43.509
put this to rest to help you all.

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:45.750
I know God has his hand on every

00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:48.550
single one of us and that if he can

00:11:48.560 --> 00:11:52.150
use me, he can use Candace.

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:53.990
You all don't remember; nobody even

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:57.350
knows me. But I want to say this: I may

00:11:57.360 --> 00:12:00.949
not have a huge platform

00:12:00.959 --> 00:12:03.750
like some of these people have,

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:05.670
but I want to ask you this

00:12:05.680 --> 00:12:07.269
for the people who really got upset at

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:11.509
me about Erica: If she was 350 lbs with

00:12:11.519 --> 00:12:13.910
a shaved head, would you still support

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:18.710
her like you do?

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:20.629
I mean, it's a hard question, but if she

00:12:20.639 --> 00:12:24.710
was 350 pounds

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:26.790
and she'd come on

00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:26.800
there—some

00:12:26.800 --> 00:12:28.790
husbands get murdered all the

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:31.670
time—but

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:33.829
a lot of times we gravitate towards

00:12:33.839 --> 00:12:36.230
the beautiful, and because it's

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:40.150
beautiful, it's perfect.

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:42.949
But does it make it perfect? It just makes

00:12:42.959 --> 00:12:46.310
it human. But if she was a really good

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:49.829
person on the inside, 350 pounds with a

00:12:49.839 --> 00:12:54.150
shaved head, would you still like her?

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:56.069
It shows the body of Christ is

00:12:56.079 --> 00:12:58.790
blinded by stupid stuff. In my

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:01.430
